contentrichtext.text: The '''Big Sandy River''' may refer to one of the following rivers in the [[United States]]: *The [[Big Sandy River (Ohio River)]], on the border between Kentucky and West Virginia *The [[Big Sandy River (Tennessee)]], a tributary of the Tennessee River *The [[Big Sandy River (Wyoming)]], a tributary of the Green River *The [[Big Sandy River (Arizona)]], a tributary of the Bill Williams River ==See also== *{{lookfrom|Big Sandy River}} *[[Big Sandy Creek (disambiguation)]] {{geodis}}
